
- Express framework to write script in server
- pg is the client tool to connect to the postgress database
- cors : ??







COMMANDS
------------------------------
npm init  : to create package.json with structure and minimum content
npm i cors express pg -s
sudo npm install touch-cli -g
npm i nodemon -g   : for hot reload
nodemon index.js







Deploy
-------------------------------------
create git repo
clone commit push
Install Heroku
heroku login
heroku --version
heroku create <name>
git push heroku <branch name> 
heroku logs --tail









